    <!-- Break Messages Level 1 -->
    <string name="break_msg_level1_1">That one step you just took will take you further. Great job.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level1_2">Just lighting the fire of focus is enough. Take a moment to catch your breath.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level1_3">It\'s okay to go slowly at your own pace. This moment is valuable enough.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level1_4">You worked hard. Why not say a warm \"Well done\" to yourself?</string>

    <!-- Break Messages Level 2 -->
    <string name="break_msg_level2_1">It was a time to raise the temperature of your heart. I can feel your sincerity.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level2_2">Your form, calmly immersed, is truly beautiful. Close your eyes and feel the peace.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level2_3">There might have been difficult moments, but you did well to focus. Please rest well.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level2_4">The scent of growth is in every place you stayed. Thank you for your hard work.</string>

    <!-- Break Messages Level 3 -->
    <string name="break_msg_level3_1">It was a time to meet yourself in deep immersion. Your passion is truly precious.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level3_2">I offer warm comfort to you, who focused on your inner self while silencing the world.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level3_3">Your back, silently keeping your place for a long time, is truly reliable and cool.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level3_4">I think I can hear your heart muscles getting stronger. You deserve a good rest.</string>

    <!-- Break Messages Level 4 -->
    <string name="break_msg_level4_1">I sincerely support you, who are so sincere about something. Your night, or day, is shining.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level4_2">It\'s impressive that you keep going without shaking even though you must be tired. Now relax and rest well.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level4_3">Like a burning bonfire, your passion is lighting up the surroundings. Thank you and well done.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level4_4">I want to gift you a relax with a warm cup of tea, who has returned from a long journey.</string>

    <!-- Break Messages Level 5 -->
    <string name="break_msg_level5_1">I pay respect to your journey beyond the limits. I believe your efforts will not be in vain.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level5_2">It was a time that shone more desperately and brilliantly than anyone else. I\'m so proud of your flame.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level5_3">You, who silently walk your own unique path in the world, are already a hero.</string>
    <string name="break_msg_level5_4">Now let everything go and stay in deep peace. Your today was perfect.</string>

